race.comment: DANCINGONMYOWN (9) is ready to make her return after a promising debut prep, most notably beaten less than a length in the LR ANZAC Day Stakes at Flemington. Readied with two solid jump-outs and is the one to beat. MARTY MCFLY (1) lines up today for the first time for trainer Tim Fitzsimmons. Two jump-outs leading in suggest he's come on nicely during the break and can make his presence felt fresh. COMMEDIA (8) hit the frame when resuming two runs back at Kilmore but couldn't back it up last start. Best figures measure up nicely. Solid top-three prospects. CAPTIVATING STORM (3) next elect. Disappointing on resuming however could represent value at big odds in this lineup having shown good form last campaign.
